description: Multiples of 3 with digits grouped in pairs and leading zeros omitted.
references: Norman Sullivan, Test Your Own IQ, Workman Publishing Co., New York, NY, 1994, pp. 54, 57.
mathematica: FromDigits /@ Partition[ Flatten[ IntegerDigits[ Table[ 3n, {n, 1, 60}]]], 2] (* _Robert G. Wilson v_ *)
author: Jason Earls (zevi_35711(AT)yahoo.com), May 06 2001
